data.description: Just a short 5-mile drive from I-24, this residence effortlessly combines comfort and accessibility. Nestled in the heart of the Fredonia Village Subdivision, this charming all-brick home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a bonus room above the spacious 2-car garage. Designed for entertaining, it offers a fenced backyard and a screened sunroom. The added convenience of a central home vacuum system makes post-gathering cleanup a breeze.
